Pete Nowlen is director of the University Concert Band. Music 43/143 meets Mondays and Wednesdays 4:006:00 p.m. 105 Music Sectional practices, TBA. Concert Band is open to nonmusic majors by audition; contact the music department at 5307525537 for further information.

Composed of 4060 wind and percussion players, the Concert Band performs exciting new band works, time tested classics, and occasional transcriptions.  The Concert Band performs every quarter in the Mondavi Center, as well as occasional tours and off campus venues.

They also have their own http://music.ucdavis.edu/concertband/ website.
